readable.content: A group of people rowing in a boat near a city . A team of rowers propel their boat forward with their paddles in the water . Five people are paddling a kayak in the ocean with the city behind them . people row in a crew boat . Very blue water with skyscraper buildings on the shore and a group of people in a canoes with paddles .
